OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAreas with weak education  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftargeted for levelling up  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Government plans would see 55          
OL,6, local-authority areas in England with  
OL,7, weak education offered extra           
OL,8, investment.                            
OL,10,FStruggling schools would be offered    
OL,11,Fmore support and new specialist        
OL,12,Fsixth-form colleges created.           
OL,14,FA target for 90% of Year 6 pupils, by  
OL,15,F2030, to pass their national curriculum
OL,16,Ftests, often known as Sats, in literacy
OL,17,Fand maths, is also planned. In 2019,   
OL,18,Ftwo-thirds reached this level.         
OL,20,FThe plans are being set out in the     
OL,21,Fgovernment's Levelling Up White Paper. 
